column1:
insert into helpdoc values(newid(), 'http://dev24.sandbox.projectinsight.net/projectinsight.webapp/api/help/model/fileitem', '

FileItem

The FileItem object contains the definition of a file (or version controlled files) in PI which appear in folders\, document folders and under tasks and other items.

NameDescriptionType
CheckOutDate Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Check Out Date] - The date/time the file was checked out.

Remarks: Read Only

 date
Comments Gets (read only) the Collection of T

Remarks: Read Only

 Collection of Comment
CreatedDateTimeUTC Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Created Date] - The date and time the item was added or generated in the system. date
CurrentVersionNumber Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [PI Version Number] - Current Version Number of the File

Remarks: Read Only

 integer
CustomFieldValue Gets (read only) the CustomFieldValue

Remarks: Read Only

 CustomFieldValue
CustomFieldValue_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT

Remarks: Default Property

 guid
Description Gets or sets the string - [Description] - The details or description of the item\, typically used to provide the user with additional information or instructions to perform the work item. string
EnableVersionControl Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Version Control] - The flag that determines whether or not version control is enabled on the file. boolean
FileName Gets or sets the string - [File Name] - The the file name of the file\, automatically handles versioning.

Remarks: Read Only\, Default Property

 string
FileType Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [File Type] - The type of file. integer
FileTypeName Gets (read only) the string string
FileVersions Gets (read only) the Collection of T - [File Versions] - The collection of previous file versions when version control is enabled.

Remarks: Read Only

 Collection of FileItemVersion
Id Gets or sets the guid Id. guid
IdExternal Gets or sets the ProjectInsight.Models.Base.ApiModelBase.IdExternal object which allows the object to be saved with an associated external identification. Used primarily for integrations. IdExternal
IsCheckedOut Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Checked Out] - The indicating whether the file is currently checked out.

Remarks: Read Only

 boolean
IsTemplate Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Template] - A template that can be re-used when creating new items. boolean
ItemContainer_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Parent Item] - The item which is the immediate parent of the current item. guid
ItemIdCopiedFrom

Remarks: Read Only

 guid
ItemNumber Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Number] - The system generated item number. integer
ItemNumberAlt Gets or sets the string - [Number Alt] - The alternate user entered item number. string
ItemNumberCombined Gets (read only) the string - [Number (Combined)] - The item number and the item number alternative combined together.

Remarks: Read Only

 string
LastComment Gets (read only) the Comment - [Last Comment] -

Remarks: Read Only

 Comment
LastComment_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Last Comment] -

Remarks: Read Only

 guid
Name Gets or sets the string - [Name] - The set of words used to refer to the item\, input by the user.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
SerializeType Get or Set if the Type should be serialized boolean
SizeKB Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Size (KB)] - The file size in kilobytes.

Remarks: Read Only

 decimal number
Type Gets or sets the string object type for external reference\, rest calls. string
UpdatedDateTimeUTC Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Updated Date] - The date and time the item was last changed or updated. date
UploadedFile Gets or sets the FileUpload which will be uploaded with file item. FileUpload
Url Gets (read only) the string - [URL] - The relative URL to the display page for the item.

Remarks: Read Only

 string
UrlDownload Gets (read only) the string - [Download Url] - The relative URL to download the physical file contents.

Remarks: Read Only\, Default Property

 string
UrlFull Gets (read only) the string - [URLFull] - The full URL to the display page for the item.

Remarks: Read Only\, Default Property

 string
UrlMobile Gets (read only) the string - [URL (mobile)] - The relative URL to the mobile display page for the item.

Remarks: Read Only

 string
UserAssignedBy Gets (read only) the User - [Assigned By] - The person who assigned the item to the current assignee

Remarks: Read Only

 User
UserAssignedBy_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Assigned By] - The person who assigned the item to the current assignee

Remarks: Read Only

 guid
UserCheckedOut Gets (read only) the User - [User Checked Out] - The user that has the file checked out.

Remarks: Read Only

 User
UserCheckedOut_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [User Checked Out] - The user that has the file checked out.

Remarks: Read Only

 guid
UserCreated Gets (read only) the User - [Created By] - The person who created the item

Remarks: Read Only

 User
UserCreated_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Created By] - The person who created the item guid
UserUpdated Gets (read only) the User - [Updated By] - The person who last updated the item

Remarks: Read Only

 User
UserUpdated_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Updated By] - The person who last updated the item guid
', getUtcDate())
